{"tid":1353190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒 你地唔搞掂八鄉班人 叫我點出黎?","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:02:14.000Z","uid":84115,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"700a273817be30b8b3b2e569a995d81a559a2085","tid":1353190,"uid":84115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:17:26.000Z","msg":"本人住元朗 算係偏武勇 <br />\n基本上 每次遊行 身體許可 我都會去<br />\n但經過今次星期日八鄉黑社會單野之後<br />\n我身邊既人 (屋企人/朋友) 都會擔心 以後遊行後會唔會發生同類事<br />\n我敢講 一日唔解決八鄉班人 首先元屯天既和理非人 肯定1唔會再出黎 剩返武勇既 都只會比八鄉既人打傷 <br />\n<br />\n所以 我再次希望咁多位住不同區既兄弟 7月27號 救救我地"},{"pid":"9ae7fa64d4eab59b16b474c79f9a6aff3ca97747","tid":1353190,"uid":84115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:18:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79b955950be5a9f1ccfd42d55261562ff75c5b2","tid":1353190,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:18:42.000Z","msg":"我係一個揸單程證落黎嘅大陸女人...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1353162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1353162</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3ea549db06ab634bda6f363e62f935ae20361559","tid":1353190,"uid":84115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:20:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9916cbbe00ec32e69187f0f36b2486373f93050","tid":1353190,"uid":5801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:20:51.000Z","msg":"一個也不能少 區區都係手足"},{"pid":"9e4334bccada0f66649a280a3acf46e7e40b7ab7","tid":1353190,"uid":84115,"like"